    'compliance.cn.name': 'China',
    'compliance.eu.desc': 'EU whole vehicle type approval under Regulation 2018/858 and all mandatory UNECE regulations — valid across all 27 EU member states plus Norway, Switzerland, and Iceland. Covers framework, braking, lighting (28 regulations), occupant protection, drivetrain, electrical safety, EMC, tyres, and advanced safety systems.',
