    'fleetnet_america.body.0': 'Cox Automotive, a Cox Automotive company, will provide comprehensive nationwide service support for Windrose US customers across',
    'fleetnet_america.body.1': 'The partnership ensures Windrose truck operators have access to reliable roadside assistance and maintenance coverage anywhere in the United States.',
