    'sinexcel_australia.body.0': 'Sinexcel and Windrose have partnered to deliver high-power charging solutions for the Australian market, ensuring fleet operators have access to fast, reliable charging infrastructure.',
    'sinexcel_australia.headline': 'Sinexcel and Windrose Partner for High-Power Charging in Australia',
