    'card.exc.windrose.establishes.windrose.park.': 'Windrose沿Noorderlaan建立Windrose Park Antwerp——歐洲首個電動車裝配基地。',
    'antwerp_port_assembly.body.0': 'Windrose has established',
    'antwerp_port_assembly.body.1': 'The facility marks a key step in Windrose\'s European manufacturing strategy, enabling local assembly and distribution of electric trucks across the continent.',
    'antwerp_port_assembly.headline': 'Port of Antwerp-Bruges Welcomes Windrose for European Assembly',
    'antwerp_port_assembly.stat_label.0': 'Location',
    'antwerp_port_assembly.stat_label.1': 'Assembly HQ',
    'antwerp_port_assembly.stat_label.2': 'Address',
    'antwerp_port_assembly.subline': 'Windrose establishes Windrose Park Antwerp along Noorderlaan — its first European electric truck assembly facility.',
    'antwerp_port_assembly.type': 'Press Release',
    'assembly.desc': 'Seven straightforward steps — any certified local partner, no specialist tooling required. Reduces logistics cost, creates local jobs, enables rapid market entry across 5 continents.',
    'assembly.h2': '簡化且在地化的最終組裝',
    'assembly.label': '在地組裝',
    'atc_2600km_netherlands_hungary.body.0': 'ATC電腦運輸與物流公司完成了從荷蘭芬洛到匈牙利布達佩斯的2,600公里往返里程碑之旅，證明了電動卡車可以媲美柴油車。',
    'atc_2600km_netherlands_hungary.body.1': '此次試驗橫跨了',
    'atc_2600km_netherlands_hungary.headline': 'ATC完成2,600公里電動卡車測試——芬洛至布達佩斯往返',
    'atc_2600km_netherlands_hungary.stat_label.0': '往返里程',
