    'kuehne_nagel_china.body.0': 'Windrose and Kuehne+Nagel China have completed a successful long-haul electric truck delivery spanning 1,300 km with 45 tonnes of cargo — pioneering low-carbon freight logistics at scale in the Chinese market.',
    'kuehne_nagel_china.body.1': 'The trial demonstrates the commercial viability of battery-electric trucks for heavy long-haul operations in one of the world\'s largest logistics markets.',
    'kuehne_nagel_china.headline': 'Windrose Pioneers Low-Carbon Logistics with Kuehne+Nagel China',
