    'uk_fastest_charging.body.0': 'Windrose has set a new charging speed record in the United Kingdom, demonstrating the truck\'s ultra-fast charging capability at a UK charging hub.',
    'uk_fastest_charging.body.1': 'The record session showcases how Windrose trucks can minimize downtime during long-haul operations, making electric freight commercially competitive with diesel.',
