    'uk_fastest_charging.body.0': 'Windrose has set a new charging speed record in the United Kingdom, demonstrating the truck\'s ultra-fast charging capability at a UK charging hub.',
    'uk_fastest_charging.body.1': 'The record session showcases how Windrose trucks can minimize downtime during long-haul operations, making electric freight commercially competitive with diesel.',
    'uk_fastest_charging.headline': 'Windrose Records Its Fastest Charging Session in the UK',
    'uk_fastest_charging.stat_label.0': 'Charge speed',
    'uk_fastest_charging.stat_label.1': 'Location',
    'uk_fastest_charging.stat_label.2': 'Capability',
    'uk_fastest_charging.subline': 'Windrose sets a new charging speed record in the United Kingdom, demonstrating the truck\'s ultra-fast charging capability.',
    'uk_fastest_charging.type': 'Press',
    'xos_us_deliveries.body.0': 'Xos Trucks will import, sell and support the',
    'xos_us_deliveries.body.1': 'The partnership marks Windrose\'s entry into the North American market through an established commercial vehicle partner with nationwide service coverage.',
